    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is what we have discussed so far:\r\n\r\n* AddressUtils.sol -> utils/Address.sol\r\n* ECRecovery.sol -> cryptography/ECDSA.sol\r\n* LimitBalance.sol -> remove it.\r\n* MerkleProof.sol -> utils/MerkleProof.sol\r\n* ReentrancyGuard.sol -> utils/ReentrancyGuard.sol\r\n* Bounty.sol -> maybe move it to bounties/BreakInvariantBounty.sol and promote the idea to get new bounties, or move it to examples, or remove it.\r\n\r\nNote that it's also a problem to just make `utils` the new garbage/all purpose bin. It might be a good step, but we should avoid filling it with many things. And if a better directory comes to mind, we should use it instead of utils.",
